#: ../../B/bogon-flux.rst:9
msgid ""
"A measure of a supposed field of :ref:`bogosity` emitted by a speaker, "
"measured by a :ref:`bogometer`\\; as a speaker starts to wander into "
"increasing bogosity a listener might say \"Warning, warning, bogon flux is "
"rising\". See :ref:`quantum-bogodynamics`\\."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`bogometer`\\ で測定される、話者から放出される\\ :ref:`bogosity`\\ "
"の想定上の場の尺度。話者がますます増大するbogosityへとさまよい込み始めると、聞き手は「警告、警告、bogon "
"fluxが上昇中」と言うかもしれない。\\ :ref:`quantum-bogodynamics`\\ を参照。"
